metadata.name: Evening in Classroom
metadata.description:
“I wanted to go home already. But i have already promised Eito-san we will going home together today. So i will just wait for him. He is sure busy today.

Nevermind. Since the weather is so good.”

Asami is an original character, living in her Little World.
